OL,3,CThe hidden crisis of mums struggling
OL,4,Cwith cocaine addiction
OL,6,FITV News' Reporter Chloe Oliver has
OL,7,Fbeen speaking to a mother about her
OL,8,Fstruggles with addiction and
OL,9,Fmotherhood after she turned to cocaine
OL,10,Fto cope.
OL,12,FA mother from Norfolk who became
OL,13,Freliant on cocaine has shared her
OL,14,Fstory with ITV News amid growing
OL,15,Fconcerns about the number of mums
OL,16,Fstruggling with secret drug addictions.
