OL,3,CThe hidden crisis of mums struggling
OL,4,Cwith cocaine addiction
OL,6,FCocaine use in the UK has doubled in
OL,7,Fthe last 20 years and cocaine use
OL,8,Famong mothers like 'Rachel' is
OL,9,Fbecoming more and more common, with
OL,10,Fmany users finding themselves in a
OL,11,Fvicious cycle of using it to escape
OL,12,Fthe emotional and psychological toll
OL,13,Fof motherhood.
OL,15,FBut, while the drug may provide a
OL,16,Ftemporary respite from reality, it is
OL,17,Foften followed by sharp declines in
OL,18,Fmood, anxiety, then feelings of guilt
OL,19,For shame.
