OL,3,CThe hidden crisis of mums struggling
OL,4,Cwith cocaine addiction
OL,6,FLester Morse, Director of Rehabs UK,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Usually it has to get pretty
OL,8,Fbad for someone to even reach out
OL,9,Fbecause of the stigma of it...And if
OL,10,Fyou've then got a mother with a child
OL,11,Fand the stigma that it's going to
OL,12,Fcreate and so that's going to be a lot
OL,13,Fmore. So they're going to wait till it
OL,14,Fgets more severe before they actually
OL,15,Fdo reach out for help."
