OL,3,CThe hidden crisis of mums struggling
OL,4,Cwith cocaine addiction
OL,6,FThe drug can exacerbate anxiety,
OL,7,Fdepression, and stress - issues that
OL,8,Fmany mothers already experience. For
OL,9,Fsome, it might begin as a coping
OL,10,Fmechanism for feeling overwhelmed or
OL,11,Fexhausted, and for others, it may stem
OL,12,Ffrom social or emotional isolation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
