OL,3,CThe hidden crisis of mums struggling
OL,4,Cwith cocaine addiction
OL,6,F'Rachel' said: "You look at our life
OL,7,Ftoday, from the moment you wake up,
OL,8,Fit's go. You have screaming kids, you
OL,9,Fhave work, you have partners, you have
OL,10,Fall of this pressure and it just
OL,11,Fbuilds and builds and builds. It's
OL,12,Fimpossible to be this perfect person,
OL,13,Fbut we want to be and we want to be a
OL,14,Fgood role model. So how do we do that?
OL,15,FWe find coping mechanisms.
OL,17,F"So I started using cocaine and and
OL,18,Ffor a long time I did use cocaine, and
OL,19,Fthen cocaine started using me."
